                                                        <p class="" style=" display: inline-block; width: auto; height: 150px; padding: 2rem; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;">Ed Fink has been battling the VA for six years. To give in to depression would “give them a victory,” Fink says.</p>
                                                    </div>
