                                                        <p class="" style=" display: inline-block; width: auto; height: 150px; padding: 2rem; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;">Mekdeci's foundation released its latest report in June on the data she has been gathering for three decades. The results were startling.</p>
                                                    </div>
